@node loadit "How To Load TB3.4"

 You can load TB3.4 from its icon.  Double Click on it and the program
 loads.

 A window will apper telling you about Telephone Book V 3.4, close this
 and the main screen will apper.

 NOTE: You can load TB3.4 by using @{" CLITB " link bugs}

 NOTE: TB3.4 needs the asl.library Version 37 in libs drawer.
       If don`t know which version you have then type this in shell:-
       'Version LIBS:asl.library'

 @{" The Menus   " link menu}
 @{" The Buttons " link 3}
 @{" Contents    " link Main}

@ENDNODE

