@ENDNODE

@node 9 "Empty Button"

 NOTE: EDC is in the MODS/ drawer and must stay here for Menu3 to
 work.

 What this button does is up to you.  Use EDC on this disk to
 edit TB3.4 config file ( TB.Config ) to change what this button does.

 Save is the arrow pointing to the disk.  disk<-
 Load is the arrow pointing away from the disk.  disk->

 Use EDC before using TB3.4 if you want your option to be used.

 Press @{" Me " System "MODS/EDC"} to run EDC now.

 @{" The Buttons " link 3}

@ENDNODE

